SELECT format(
    $1 || $2 ||
    $3 || $4,
    col, col, col, col, col, col
)
FROM unnest(ARRAY[$5, $6, $7, $8, $9, $10]) AS col
WHERE EXISTS (SELECT $11 FROM information_schema.columns WHERE table_schema = $12 AND table_name = $13 AND column_name = col)
